348
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:45,100
No.

349
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:46,580
It's quite good.

350
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:52,060
Then, what about...

351
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:56,260
(Zhou Ye)

352
00:19:56,260 --> 00:19:58,100
(There is no soccer match
on the campus today.)

353
00:19:58,150 --> 00:19:59,460
(We're at an internet café.)

354
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,390
