360
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,720
I need to head back to school.

361
00:20:27,390 --> 00:20:27,780
Alright.

362
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,780
I'll take you back then.

363
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:29,340
It's fine.

364
00:20:29,390 --> 00:20:30,580
I can go back on my own.

365
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,300
Waiter, I want to pay the bill, please.

366
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,080
I'll pay for this.

367
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:34,540
Don't you have something urgent to do?

368
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,340
You should go first.

369
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:35,880
Well...

370
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,390
Next time...

371
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:38,520
It's my treat next time.

372
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:39,500
Thank you, Tian Chi.

373
00:20:40,260 --> 00:20:40,630
Huan'er,

374
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:43,470
