375
00:20:43,870 --> 00:20:45,260
If you're done with your plans,

376
00:20:45,990 --> 00:20:46,780
come and find me.

377
00:20:47,870 --> 00:20:48,390
Alright.

378
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:50,630
I'm sorry, Tian Chi.

379
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:52,060
I'll contact you later.

380
00:20:52,260 --> 00:20:52,630
Alright.

381
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,300
Jing Xichi.

382
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:21,470
Wait there.

383
00:21:23,100 --> 00:21:25,580
