and you're not answering!

384
00:21:25,580 --> 00:21:27,430
What kind of big business
do you have now?

385
00:21:28,190 --> 00:21:29,300
I was playing soccer

386
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:30,390
and didn't bring my phone.

387
00:21:31,260 --> 00:21:33,340
You don't look like
you have just played soccer.

388
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,540
Well, maybe it's just because

389
00:21:36,540 --> 00:21:37,860
I was born naturally good-looking.

390
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:39,780
Don't pretend.

391
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:41,150
I can smell your shampoo.

392
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,140
What's wrong with you?

393
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,260
Are you going through a breakup?

394
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:53,060
A breakup?

395
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:55,870
Do you think I'll go through a breakup?

396
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:58,980
Oh yeah, now you're a star
in Computer Science Department.

397
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:00,260
It's different from before.

398
00:22:00,630 --> 00:22:01,870
I'm in high demand now.

399
00:22:02,230 --> 00:22:02,670
Exactly.

400
00:22:03,740 --> 00:22:04,950
I even heard about

401
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:06,100
that pink rose incident.

402
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:07,580
Did someone confess to you?

403
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:11,390
I turned her down.

404
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:14,260
Why?

405
00:22:16,260 --> 00:22:17,580
Don't you think she looks a lot

406
00:22:17,670 --> 00:22:19,260
like our high school English teacher?

407
00:22:20,390 --> 00:22:21,260
Does she?

408
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,710
Du Wei is quite pretty, though.

409
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,200
I'm not talking about her look.

410
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,740
It's just

411
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:26,580
her charm.

412
00:22:27,630 --> 00:22:29,190
She always seems all smiley,

413
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,910
but deep down, she's super serious.

414
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:32,390
I'm scared I'd dream

415
00:22:32,390 --> 00:22:33,190
about her forcing me

416
00:22:33,190 --> 00:22:34,780
to finish up an English practice set.

417
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:37,820
You're nuts.

418
00:22:39,870 --> 00:22:40,870
Speaking of that,

419
00:22:41,630 --> 00:22:42,740
why did you go for Tian Chi?

420
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:43,580
He seems like

421
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:44,540
such a boring guy.

422
00:22:44,990 --> 00:22:46,150
I'm just trying it out.

423
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:47,870
You never know

424
00:22:47,910 --> 00:22:49,150
what you like until you try.

425
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:51,500
If you wanted to try,

426
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:52,950
did it have to be him?

427
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,620
If you wanted to try
dating a top student,

428
00:22:54,620 --> 00:22:55,760
you could've picked Song.

429
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:56,950
Are you out of your mind?

430
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:00,780
Oh, you're mad.

431
00:23:00,950 --> 00:23:01,670
No, I'm not.

432
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:02,340
You're mad.

433
00:23:02,430 --> 00:23:03,340
I'm not!

434
00:23:03,430 --> 00:23:04,430
You must be mad.

435
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,820
I brought you a lot of snacks.

436
00:23:09,740 --> 00:23:11,230
Come on, I'm an adult now.

437
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:12,430
I don't eat these.

438
00:23:12,540 --> 00:23:13,710
I got you a ton of chips!

439
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,540
Why there is no
Little Raccoon's crunchy noodles?

440
00:23:17,230 --> 00:23:18,340
The school convenience store

441
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:19,430
doesn't sell them anymore.

442
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:26,540
The favorite restaurants close down.

443
00:23:26,950 --> 00:23:28,540
The favorite snacks disappear.

444
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,190
Why does this happen?

445
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:38,150
You can try new snacks.

446
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:39,430
This one's really good.

447
00:23:47,780 --> 00:23:48,390
How is it?

448
00:23:48,540 --> 00:23:49,230
Is it good?

449
00:23:49,230 --> 00:23:49,950
It's good.

450
00:23:50,390 --> 00:23:51,390
It tastes good.

451
00:23:52,950 --> 00:23:54,020
But, some things

452
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:56,230
just can't be replaced.

453
00:23:58,300 --> 00:23:58,910
Right?

454
00:24:05,300 --> 00:24:05,910
Yeah.

455
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:11,710
If you like it,

456
00:24:11,710 --> 00:24:13,220
I'll buy you another pack next time.

457
00:24:13,630 --> 00:24:14,230
Just one pack?

458
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:15,990
One pack isn't enough?

459
00:24:16,430 --> 00:24:17,430
You're so stingy.

460
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:19,580
You say me stingy?

461
00:24:19,710 --> 00:24:22,100
Remember back in high school
when we got robbed?

462
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:23,580
You bought only one can of Jianlibao

463
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:24,780
and shared it with Song Cong,

464
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:25,960
but you didn't let me drink.

465
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:28,020
Do you remember this tiny thing?

466
00:24:28,060 --> 00:24:28,950
Of course, I do.

467
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:29,630
I hold grudges.

468
00:24:29,630 --> 00:24:31,150
Do you remember the agriculture study,

469
00:24:31,430 --> 00:24:33,150
I gave you everything I had?

470
00:24:33,150 --> 00:24:34,060
Lies!

471
00:24:34,150 --> 00:24:35,230
You had half of it

472
00:24:35,230 --> 00:24:36,540
but shared it with Song Cong.

473
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:38,470
You forgot?

474
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:38,990
Did it?

475
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,140
You really don't remember?

476
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:40,870
I don't think so.

477
00:24:40,870 --> 00:24:42,360
It did! Don't try to weasel out of it.

478
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:42,740
No way.

479
00:24:42,820 --> 00:24:44,160
I swear I gave it all to you.

480
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:45,780
Hold this for me.

481
00:24:50,820 --> 00:24:51,500
Oh no!

482
00:24:53,340 --> 00:24:54,060
(Tian Chi)

483
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:56,430
Hello, Huan'er.

484
00:24:57,430 --> 00:24:58,990
Sorry, are you still there?

485
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,540
Did you already come?

486
00:25:00,990 --> 00:25:02,060
I'm sorry.

487
00:25:04,670 --> 00:25:06,300
How about we go there another day?

488
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:08,300
Alright.

489
00:25:08,470 --> 00:25:09,710
Sorry.

490
00:25:10,820 --> 00:25:12,500
Rest early.

491
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:14,950
Alright.

492
00:25:15,870 --> 00:25:16,390
Bye.

493
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:29,340
(Utopia Bar)

494
00:25:36,670 --> 00:25:37,340
Uh...

495
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:38,910
I'm heading back.

496
00:25:39,340 --> 00:25:40,540
They are about to rest now.

497
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,200
What about you?

498
00:25:45,670 --> 00:25:47,020
I'll just stay here for a bit.

499
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:01,580
Bye.

500
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:10,190
Jing Xichi,

501
00:26:10,390 --> 00:26:11,670
what are you doing?

502
00:26:21,950 --> 00:26:23,060
Tian Chi,

503
00:26:24,870 --> 00:26:25,910
why are you here?

504
00:26:26,870 --> 00:26:27,300
Huan'er,

505
00:26:28,430 --> 00:26:29,260
actually, today I do

506
00:26:30,100 --> 00:26:31,100
have something

507
00:26:31,670 --> 00:26:32,820
I wanted to tell you.

508
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:35,340
I...

509
00:26:37,060 --> 00:26:38,780
I also have something to tell you.

510
00:26:38,910 --> 00:26:39,870
Let me finish first.

511
00:26:40,700 --> 00:26:42,760
I'm afraid that if I don't say it now,

512
00:26:43,150 --> 00:26:44,230
I won't get another chance.

513
00:26:50,540 --> 00:26:51,150
I am

514
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:53,020
not good with words,

515
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:55,990
but for some reason,

516
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:57,870
every time I see you,

517
00:26:58,670 --> 00:26:59,780
I become nervous

518
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:01,980
which makes me unable to deliver

519
00:27:02,150 --> 00:27:03,020
what I want to say.

520
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:05,100
Even when I do,

521
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:06,540
they never come out right.

522
00:27:07,910 --> 00:27:08,950
So,

523
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:11,100
whenever we part,

524
00:27:11,150 --> 00:27:12,230
I regret it,

525
00:27:14,500 --> 00:27:15,870
thinking I didn't do enough.

526
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:21,870
I always believed

527
00:27:22,430 --> 00:27:23,260
that feelings

528
00:27:23,820 --> 00:27:24,470
should

529
00:27:24,470 --> 00:27:25,710
happen naturally.

530
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:27,740
I think there's a long way to go.

531
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:30,100
And, as time goes,

532
00:27:30,740 --> 00:27:31,300
the two people

533
00:27:31,300 --> 00:27:32,640
will eventually become closer.

534
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:36,340
But, I realized I was wrong.

535
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,260
I know

536
00:27:41,780 --> 00:27:43,100
there is someone very important

537
00:27:43,340 --> 00:27:44,910
in your heart.

538
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:47,870
But unfortunately,

539
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:50,190
the person isn't me.

540
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:04,780
I'm sorry,

541
00:28:06,670 --> 00:28:07,470
Tian Chi.

542
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:11,260
Maybe you're right.

543
00:28:13,670 --> 00:28:14,540
Right now,

544
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,470
I really

545
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:18,580
can't like anyone else.

546
00:28:25,150 --> 00:28:25,870
I should return

547
00:28:27,540 --> 00:28:28,540
this book to you.

548
00:28:30,390 --> 00:28:31,580
Things that don't belong to me

549
00:28:32,470 --> 00:28:33,390
shouldn't be kept.

550
00:28:36,230 --> 00:28:37,020
I also hope

551
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:38,630
you find

552
00:28:38,710 --> 00:28:39,540
your own happiness.

553
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,470
I wish you happiness too.

554
00:28:57,190 --> 00:28:57,710
Sincerely.

555
00:29:02,430 --> 00:29:03,190
Then...

556
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:04,870
I get to go now.

557
00:29:48,630 --> 00:29:50,150
You seem in a good mood.

558
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:51,260
What happened?

559
00:29:51,540 --> 00:29:53,020
Tian Chi confessed to you?

560
00:29:53,540 --> 00:29:54,100
Yeah.

561
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,470
You're not single anymore...

562
00:29:57,470 --> 00:29:58,430
I turned him down.

563
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,540
I knew it.

564
00:30:02,540 --> 00:30:03,630
Why?

565
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:06,020
He's such a great guy.
Why don't you like him?

566
00:30:06,990 --> 00:30:08,340
Li said,

567
00:30:08,990 --> 00:30:10,300
don't ever ask why you love,

568
00:30:10,470 --> 00:30:11,950
and also why you don't.

569
00:30:12,950 --> 00:30:13,580
Good girl.

570
00:30:15,870 --> 00:30:17,500
What does that mean?

571
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:18,990
I know this one!

572
00:30:19,660 --> 00:30:21,470
In White Horse Neighs
in the Western Wind,

573
00:30:21,580 --> 00:30:22,670
Li Wenxiu mentions

574
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:26,430
they are all wonderful people.

575
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:28,060
But, I just

576
00:30:28,710 --> 00:30:29,630
don't like them.

577
00:30:31,190 --> 00:30:32,430
But, some things

578
00:30:32,630 --> 00:30:34,100
just can't be replaced.

579
00:30:36,060 --> 00:30:36,670
Right?

580
00:30:42,630 --> 00:30:43,150
Yeah.

581
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,340
Come on.

582
00:31:01,630 --> 00:31:02,340
